  m_text: 'Pressing buttons / Checkpoint: "Telephone button noise" - Caitlyn_100
    (freesounds.org)

    Gaining health or energy: "Itemize" - Scrampunk_ (freesounds.org)

    Damage:
    "Damage sound effect" - Raclure (freesounds.org)

    Shoot: "FX - Laser Shoot
    (A)" - bolkmar (freesounds.org)

    Bullet missed: "Error" - Autistic Lucario
    (freesounds.org)

    Mortar attack: "Cannon1" - Isaac200000 (freesounds.org)

    Lightbulb
    blackout: "Shock_One" - Nodgez (freesounds.org)

    Walls appearing: "power_up"
    - 400 Sounds Pack (ci.itch.io)

    Walls disappearing: "power_down" - 400 Sounds
    Pack (ci.itch.io)

    Freeze: "Ice Shatter SFX" - ImATaco (freesounds.org)

    Burn:
    "fire_lighting" - 400 Sounds pack (ci.itch.io)

    Deplete: "fall_quick" - 400
    Sounds Pack (ci.itch.io)

    Jammed: "ding" - Daphne in Wonderland (freesounds.org)

    Warp
    and Home: "Time Warp effect" - chinomaker (freesounds.org)

    Winning: "win"
    - David819 (freesounds.org)

    Losing: "energy deactivation" - d777_hickoryyy
    (freesounds.org)'
